These are Puzzles for 7x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 7x4-Level-7-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, sprite, juice, tea
The people have 4 different jobs:  coach, librarian, pilot, videographer
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: horror, mystery, time-travel, zombie
There are 4 different nationalities: japanese, polish, spanish, turkish
4 different pets are kept: cat, chinchilla, hamster, mouse
4 different games are played: backgammon, canasta, scrabble, billiard
There are 4 different favourite colors: ivory, orange, apricot, coral
 1. the turkish is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1
 2. the person watching mystery movies is the owner of the cat##1
 3. the person drinking juice is not the person who likes orange##6
 4. the person who likes apricot is not the person drinking sprite##6
 5. the turkish is somewhere to the left of the person playing scrabble##5
 6. the owner of the cat is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3
 7. the person who likes coral is not the person playing canasta##6
 8. the japanese is the coach##1
 9. the pilot is not the person drinking tea##6
10. the videographer is the person who likes orange##1
11. the pilot is the person who likes ivory##1
12. the owner of the cat is on the far right##1
13. the person who likes coral is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
14. the owner of the hamster is somewhere to the right of the librarian##5
15. the polish is on the right of the person watching horror movies##1
16. the person who likes apricot is somewhere between the person who likes orange and the person who likes coral##7
17. the person playing billiard is not the japanese##6
18. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
19. the person playing canasta is somewhere between the coach and the person playing backgammon##7
20. the owner of the chinchilla is not the person drinking tea##6
21. the videographer is somewhere to the left of the pilot##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |    3     |     4     |
| Beverage          | iced-tea      | tea   | sprite     | juice |
| Job           | videographer | librarian   | coach    | pilot     |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie       | time-travel | horror   | mystery   |
| Nationality   | spanish      | turkish     | japanese | polish    |
| Pet           | chinchilla   | mouse       | hamster  | cat       |
| Game         | backgammon     | canasta     | scrabble | billiard   |
| Color     | orange          | apricot      | coral     | ivory      |

